2x RJ-11 voice ports for analog phones or fax machines :with two independent telephone numbers. This device appears to be using the same board as the [[Linksys WRT54GP2A-AT]], :though the miniPCI slot is not populated on this model. The OS used on this device is presumed to be the same (''VxWorks'') :as the WRT54GP2's (and other derivative models).
